          <div class="prose">
            <p class="updated">Last updated: 1 July 2026</p>

            <p>The Fragrance Secrets is a UAE-based fragrance retailer. This Payment Policy explains the ways you can pay for orders placed on thefragrancesecrets.com, how each method works, and how we protect your payment details. By placing an order with us, you agree to the terms set out below. All prices, charges and refunds referenced on this page are in United Arab Emirates Dirhams (AED) and are inclusive of VAT where applicable.</p>

            <h2 id="methods">Accepted Payment Methods</h2>
            <p>We offer a range of trusted, secure payment options so you can choose whatever suits you best — pay on delivery, pay now by card or wallet, or split the cost interest-free. All methods are available at checkout for eligible orders across the UAE.</p>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Cash on Delivery (COD)</strong> — pay the courier in cash when your order arrives, available UAE-wide across all seven Emirates.</li>
              <li><strong>Visa &amp; Mastercard</strong> — pay securely with any valid credit or debit card through our encrypted checkout.</li>
              <li><strong>Apple Pay &amp; Google Pay</strong> — check out in seconds using the wallet already on your phone, with no card numbers to type.</li>
              <li><strong>Tabby — Pay in 4</strong> — split your order into four interest-free payments over time.</li>
              <li><strong>Tamara — Split in 3</strong> — divide your total into three interest-free instalments.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>The exact options shown at checkout may vary by order value, delivery area and product type. Any applicable charges are always displayed clearly before you confirm payment — we never add hidden fees afterwards.</p>

            <h2 id="cod">How Cash on Delivery Works</h2>
            <p>Cash on Delivery is one of our most popular ways to pay, because you settle up only once your fragrance is in your hands. It is available on eligible orders anywhere in the UAE.</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Select <strong>Cash on Delivery</strong> at checkout and place your order as normal — no card details are required.</li>
              <li>Your order total, including delivery where applicable, is shown before you confirm so you know exactly what to prepare.</li>
              <li>Please have the <strong>exact amount ready in cash</strong> for the courier, as drivers may not always carry change.</li>
              <li>Payment is collected at the door when your parcel is handed over. Any COD handling charge, where relevant, is displayed at checkout.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>To keep delivery smooth, please make sure your address and contact number are correct and that someone is available to receive the order and complete payment. If a COD handover cannot be completed after repeated attempts, the order may be returned to us and we will contact you to arrange re-delivery.</p>

            <h2 id="bnpl">Buy Now, Pay Later</h2>
            <p>Love a fragrance but prefer to spread the cost? We partner with <strong>Tabby</strong> and <strong>Tamara</strong> — the UAE's leading Buy Now, Pay Later providers — so you can split your purchase into smaller, <strong>interest-free</strong> instalments with no hidden fees when you pay on time.</p>
            <h3>How the instalments work</h3>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Tabby — Pay in 4:</strong> your order total is divided into four equal payments. You pay the first at checkout and the rest across the following weeks.</li>
              <li><strong>Tamara — Split in 3:</strong> your total is split into three equal monthly payments, with the first taken at checkout.</li>
              <li>Both options are <strong>0% interest</strong> when payments are made on schedule — you never pay more than the product price.</li>
            </ul>
            <h3>Eligibility</h3>
            <p>Buy Now, Pay Later is subject to approval by Tabby or Tamara at the time of checkout. To use it you will typically need to be a UAE resident, meet a minimum order value, and complete a quick eligibility check with the provider. Approval, credit limits and any late-payment terms are determined solely by Tabby and Tamara under their own terms and conditions, which you accept when you choose their service. If an instalment plan is declined, you can simply complete your order using Cash on Delivery, card or wallet instead.</p>

            <h2 id="security">Card &amp; Wallet Security</h2>
            <p>Your security is a priority at every step. When you pay by card or digital wallet, your payment is processed through a <strong>PCI-DSS compliant</strong> payment gateway using industry-standard encryption.</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Card and wallet details are entered on a secure, encrypted payment page and transmitted directly to our payment processor.</li>
              <li><strong>We do not store your full card number</strong> on our servers — sensitive payment data stays with the certified gateway.</li>
              <li>Card payments may be protected by <strong>3-D Secure</strong> (such as a one-time password from your bank) for an extra layer of verification.</li>
              <li>Apple Pay and Google Pay use device-level tokenisation, so your real card number is never shared with us.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>We will never ask you to share your full card number, PIN or one-time password over WhatsApp, email or phone. If you ever receive such a request claiming to be from us, please do not respond and contact our team straight away.</p>

            <h2 id="currency">Currency &amp; VAT</h2>
            <p>All prices on thefragrancesecrets.com are listed and charged in <strong>United Arab Emirates Dirhams (AED)</strong>.</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Prices shown are <strong>inclusive of 5% VAT</strong> where applicable, in line with UAE tax regulations.</li>
              <li>The price you see at checkout is the price you pay — there are no surprise currency conversions on the total we charge.</li>
              <li>If you pay with a card issued outside the UAE, your bank may apply its own foreign-exchange or processing fees, which are beyond our control.</li>
              <li>A VAT-compliant tax summary is included with your order confirmation; a full tax invoice is available on request.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 id="failed">Failed &amp; Declined Payments</h2>
            <p>Occasionally a card or wallet payment may not go through. This is almost always resolved quickly. Common reasons include:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Insufficient funds or an exceeded card limit.</li>
              <li>An expired card, or incorrectly entered card or billing details.</li>
              <li>Your bank declining the transaction or requiring 3-D Secure verification.</li>
              <li>A temporary connection issue between your bank and the payment gateway.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>If your payment is declined, your order will not be confirmed and no goods will be dispatched — but you may still see a temporary authorisation hold from your bank, which is released automatically within a few working days. You are welcome to try again, use a different card or wallet, or simply switch to <strong>Cash on Delivery</strong>. If you continue to have trouble, our team is happy to help you complete your order.</p>

            <h2 id="refunds">Refunds to Original Method</h2>
            <p>When a refund is due under our Return &amp; Refund Policy, we process it back to the <strong>original payment method</strong> wherever possible, so your money returns the same way it left.</p>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Card, Apple Pay &amp; Google Pay:</strong> refunds are returned to the card or wallet used at checkout.</li>
              <li><strong>Tabby &amp; Tamara:</strong> refunds are processed through the provider, which adjusts or cancels your remaining instalments accordingly.</li>
              <li><strong>Cash on Delivery:</strong> as no card is on file, COD refunds are issued by bank transfer or store credit — whichever you prefer.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Once a refund is approved, we initiate it promptly. The time it takes to appear in your account depends on your bank or BNPL provider, and is typically a few working days. We will confirm by email or WhatsApp the moment your refund has been processed on our side.</p>

            <h2 id="contact">Contact Us</h2>
            <p>Have a question about a payment, an instalment plan or a refund? Our team is here to help:</p>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>WhatsApp:</strong> chat with our team any day from 10am to 7pm — <a href="#" onclick="waChat();return false">start a WhatsApp chat</a>.</li>
              <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:info@thefragrancesecrets.com">info@thefragrancesecrets.com</a></li>
              <li><strong>Contact page:</strong> visit our <a href="/pages/contact">Contact page</a> for all the ways to reach us.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

